divs: sighting detailsdear sirs, attached are three photos. i was taking pictures of the rainbow and i did not see the ufo's until after i had downloaded the pictures to my computer. i took these pictures on the evening of tuesday, july 7, 2009 at about 7:00 pm cdt. they were of the eastern sky about 70-75 degree above the horizon. thank you, *(wit's name removed--cms\sg) satsuma, alabama
